Package interfaces

public interfaces for defining the model of how the keywordProvider works with keywords, logging, and Excel workbooks.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    CheckedRunnable
    Interface for being able to check if a Runnable object throws an exception
    IAAALogEvent
    Model for log events for Triple AAA Logging pattern which includes Arrange, Act, Assert, and optionally Cleanup sections of a test case Classes that implement this interface are designed to create log events for these 4 sections of a test case
    IAction
    Interface for KeywordProvider provided Action Keywords.
    IAfterAction
    IAfterAction is a way to perform an Action Keywords a given number of times until the expected outcome is achieved.
    IAssert
    KeywordProvider provided Assert Keywords Assert Keywords are any keywords intended to perform a validation that can pass or fail a Test Case.
    IGet
    Interface for KeywordProvider provided Get Keywords.
    IKeyword<T>
    The IKeyword interface is the base model for all of the KeywordProvider Selenium Keywords.
    ILogging
    Primary interface used for Logging within the keywordProvider Logging is designed to use an interface so that any type of logging library can be used without issues of refactoring.
    ITestCase
    Model used by the keywordProvider to allow for various types of Non-coded test design like Excel spreadsheets and JSON files This Interface models a Test Case and includes methods for getting information about a Test Case
    ITestRunner
    Primary interface model for executing ITestCase implementations This Interface will run KeywordProvider Keywords, Custom created Keywords, and Page Object methods
    ITestStep
    Model used by the keywordProvider to allow for various types of Non-coded test design like Excel spreadsheets and JSON files This interface models a single test step as part of an ITestCase.
    ITouchAction  
    IWait
    KeywordProvider provided Wait Keywords Wait Keywords are any keyword intended delay the execution of Selenium until some specific condition is met.

Package interfaces Description

public interfaces for defining the model of how the keywordProvider works with keywords, logging, and Excel workbooks.
